Liono Flash past the maximals Carrying Dark and the Lion to the Cr Chambers 
"Its seems everything almost normal." Scans the area. "Good Job maximals." 
Goes to his Quarters and puts Dark in his Private Cr Chamber. Then examines 
the Lion and thinks well I can't fix him I wonder Put him inside the CR 
Chamber. "Here goes nothing."

As Liono goes to the next Cr Chamber. While he reviews all the reports on 
events. "Iron and Prowl handle themselves well."
